name: Katherine Barrett
text: This is just lovely!  We were the only ones there and the kids really had a blast.  It's FREE!

name: Donna Murphy
text: Had a great time with my granddaughter

name: John Carlisle
text: Great spot to let the kids cool off on a hot day. Just dont trust the coke machine as it likes to keep money and not dispense drinks.

name: Rachel Livingston
text: It was a nice splash pad! I wish the shaded seating was where you could see the whole splash pad and some areas were slick so some of the kids slipped and fell. Overall it was a nice place.

name: Johnny Workhorse
text: Great place for the kids to run wild. Unlike other splash pads if visited this one is fenced which seems safer. Only thing lacking is shade since adults aren't allowed in water they sit and scorch.

name: Samantha Watts
text: My kids love this place. Could benefit from some tables and more shade.

name: Nicole Harrell
text: Kool place for parties and  togetherness then play in the fountain

name: Chuck White
text: Good place for the kids to play

name: Misty Merilien
text: Fun and free!

text:

name: Barry Pollard
text: It was the county fair about the same the food was good. The rides for the adults was better this year lot more kids rides More security

name: Daniel Lucas
text: Awesome venue, and the soccer fields are very well kept.  The staff are super friendly and helpful!

text: Prefer golf course. Can't see how this was a better money generator....

text: We love this new park! Best place for walking/running in Huntsville.
